name: Little Pig pendant
description: Little Pig is a pendant light cheekily simple but unmistakably beauty, and spirit. This playful lamp comfortably fits a variety of different settings, whether a formal environment. This versatile pendant features a double light source for maximum impact.

name: Clover stool 42
description: Clover, a delightful little plywood stool, will bring fun and function and a good measure of luck. It comes flat packed for easy assembly and is stackable.

name: anise stool
description: Anise stool adds spice to your life with its vibrant, expressive form. Inspired by nature’s own creation the star anise, the Anise stool immortalizes this unique form is this beautifully shaped stool. Creating an immediate convivial atmosphere suited to indoor and outdoor environments with a design, the self-draining Anise is made from durable polyethylene, a recyclable and UV resistant plastic.

name: Yhi from
description:
Yhi 720/ 1080 Pendant Lamp

The Yhi lamp is imbued with an inspirational sculptural beauty.
With a firm commitment to sustainability, Yhi’s radiant form
inspires its name which is an indigenous word meaning ‘sun goddess’. Locally designed and manufactured from plantation harvested plywood, Yhi is 100% recyclable. The magnificent attention to detail of Yhi is carried through to its flat-packed assembly which minimises its environmental impact and carbon footprint through reduced transportation costs, making it green star friendly with a cool, chic, savvy to boot.

Available in 720mm and 1080mm diameter.

name: coral planter 120
description: The Coral planter brings with it a unique style and panache, and with three sizes, the Coral planter cradles flowers and plants, presenting them in an elevated position. A specialised self-watering system ensures plants enjoy extended life and beauty, and look their best for longer. Suited to both indoor and outdoor environments Coral is made from durable polyethylene, a recyclable and UV resistant plastic, and comes in a range of warm earthy colours. Perfect with the Coral Seating.

name: orbit candelabra
description:
The Orbit’s playful elegance is born of its innate simplicity. In plan
the pure circular form is manipulated so subtly, its true undulating
nature is revealed only in being. The Orbit rests elegantly on any
surface, its tripod configuration producing stability and practicality.
Fabricated in polished solid steel rod, this designer piece is the
perfect foil for that intimate candlelit setting.

name: cero
description: Winner of a 2003 Australian Design Award, the cero chair is a captivating union between form and function. Simple lines imbue this timeless piece with an elegance that catches the eye and provokes a smile. The streamlined Cero features a stylish central void while its distinctive nibble elicits an uncontrollable desire to take a seat. Adaptable to both internal as well as external environments in recyclable polyethylene plastic.

name: subCero
description: subCero is the sibling of the internationally successful Cero chair, a 2003 Australian Design Award winner. subCero has a playful elegance with its sculptural union between form and function. The stylish central void distributes forces applied to the seat throughout the circular form giving strength and robustness. Importantly for young children sharp edges have been eliminated and a unique ergonomically designed nibble in the top of the chair encourages good posture. Adaptable to both internal as well as external environments in recyclable polyethylene plastic.

name: chuckel jr
description:
Chuckel junior is an elegant yet playful stool that suits many environments. It is light, easy to move, stackable and above all comfortable. Adaptable to both internal as well as external environments, Chuckel is fabricated in UV resistant recyclable plastic. Chuckel junior dynamically locks together function, beauty and spirit.

“Every child has the right to rest and leisure, to engage in play and recreational activities and to participate freely in cultural life and the arts.” The United Nations Convention on the Rights of the Child- Article 31

name: chuckel tables from
description:
Chuckel Low and Dine tables dynamically locks together function, beauty and spirit.  Designed to compliment the Chuckel Jr, the Low table is light and easy to move. Chuckel Dine is an elegant yet playful table that suits many environments, and is perfect teamed with Chuckel stools. 

Adaptable to both internal as well as external environments, Chuckel Low and Dine is fabricated in UV resistant recyclable plastic, with a grey compact laminate top. 

Chuckel Low & Dine tables are available with a 75cm or 90cm diameter table top. Colours available refer to the table base. 

“Every child has the right to rest and leisure, to engage in play and recreational activities and to participate freely in cultural life and the arts.” The United Nations Convention on the Rights of the Child- Article 31

name: chuckel
description: Chuckel – a little bit of outdoors…a whole lot of fun. Chuckel is an elegant yet playful stool that suits many environments. It is light, easy to move, stackable and above all comfortable. Adaptable to both internal as well as external environments, Chuckel is fabricated in UV resistant recyclable plastic. Chuckel dynamically locks together function, beauty and spirit.

name: dove44 & dove77 from
description:
Dove is flight captured in a chair. Dove’s versatility allows us to bring a sense of grace to our lives and can be sat upon from different directions, stacked quickly, and moved at a moments notice. Quick, convenient and dynamic, the Dove wire stools come in a variety of heights including 44cm and 77cm, ideal for café, bar or residential environments. 
Comes either in a zinc finish or can be powder coated if you want a colour!

Dove bar stools come either in a zinc finish or can be powder coated in three stunning colours!

name: pinch 44 from
description: Pinch is a magically simple stool with a delicious belly draping down to a cruciform shape. By rotating the stool it can be conveniently and securely stacked. Available in a range of polyethylene plastic colours to suit all occasions Pinch is the answer when simplicity is required.

name: pinch 66&77 from
description: Pinch 66&77 bar stool brings a unique style and panache to suit any decor. Suited to both indoor and outdoor environments Coral seating is made from durable polyethylene, a recyclable and UV resistant plastic.

name: proost coasters
description:
Proost Coasters are a collection of uniquely styled ‘intelligent’ coasters fusing green responsibility with classic ‘steendyk’ signature patterns.

The Proost Coasters are made from earth friendly and 100% recyclable ceramic, to absorb moisture from condensation or drips, and eliminating the problem of coasters sticking to the bottom of your glass or cup.

Available in five striking ‘signature’ designs, these coasters will add a touch of sophistication and class to any setting.

name: wave coat hangers x3  from
description:
The Wave clothes hanger is an ingenious new spin on the humble clothes hanger creating an asymmetric and dynamic form, while losing nothing of the functionality required. Suitable for hanging a whole array of different garments in different ways. 

Comes in a pack of three.

name: spinout bathplug
description:
For those who appreciate the nuances of luxury design, the Spinout
plug is the finishing touch to the streamlined contemporary
bathroom. Its sinuous profile is ergonomically designed in
polypropylene for the ultimate commune between function and
aesthetics. Available in both 60 and 80 millimetre diameter, the
Spinout is bath ware at its bijoux finest.

name: wave rack
description:
The Wave clothes rack is an inventive new space saving rack that removes the protruding stabilising legs of contemporary clothes racks. The simple fluid line of the base contrasts elegantly with the vertical and horizontal rail, marrying beautifully together to form a gracefully dancing ribbon of steel.

Made from stainless steel tube and easily assembled in a matter of minutes without the need for tools, the Wave clothes rack can be combined with the Wave clothes hanger to ideally suit elegant hotels, office receptions or the contemporary home where style is important.

name: anise 280 lamp
description: Throwing a constellation through its laser cut pattern onto the walls, Anise Pendant is both simple and beautiful. Fabricated from a delicate sheet of etched brass, the anise lamp is 28cm high.

name: anise bookmark
description: simple, elegant and engaging. This beautiful bookmark follows in the Anise Pendant Lamp's footsteps. The beautiful warm colour of the brass is etched with a delicate pattern. Available also in blackened brass and stainless steel. Great as a gift.

name: anise earrings from
description: These beautiful earrings follow in the Anise Pendant Lamp's footsteps. The beautiful warm colour of the brass is etched with a delicate pattern. Available also in blackened brass and stainless steel. Great as a gift.

name: sunray sun lounge
description: Sunray is a blissful lounge designed specifically for relaxation in a fashion well suited to the antipodean ‘bronzed aussie’ ethos. Inspired by the languid form of the manta ray, the Sunray lounge is ergonomically engineered to maximise comfort and exude luxury for those who know the meaning of indulgence and repose. Ideal for hedonistic poolside environments. Sunray can be stacked away at a moments notice.

name: coral 4 pce configuration
description:
The Coral seating brings with it a unique style and panache, and a multitude of possibilities. The curved seat and seat end join together, allowing a wide variety of configurations to suit your needs. Suited to both indoor and outdoor environments Coral seating is made from durable polyethylene, a recyclable and UV resistant plastic.

The Coral 4 piece configuration comes with two curved seat parts and two seat ends to form a C or an S-shape.

name: coral 4pce planter configuration
description:
The Coral seating brings with it a unique style and panache, and a multitude of possibilities. The curved seat, seat end and planter end join together, allowing a wide variety of configurations to suit your needs. The gentle angle of the planter end further provides a comfortable back-rest to enjoy a respite from the busy day. A specialised self-watering system ensures plants enjoy extended life and beauty, and look their best for longer. Suited to both indoor and outdoor environments Coral seating is made from durable polyethylene, a recyclable and UV resistant plastic.

The Coral 4 piece planter configuration comes with two curved seat parts, a seat end and a planter end to form a C or an S-shape.
